snippet.description:

Rocket Beans TV ist ein Creator-Kollektiv rund um Gaming, digitale Popkultur und Unterhaltung. Bei uns findest du spannende Let's Plays, interaktive Formate wie Chat Duell, das Kinomagazin Kino+, exklusive Events und vieles mehr. snippet.title: Jenders Gaming
snippet.description:
Welcome to the channel! 
Here it's all about Board games, card games, miniature games, and wargaming. If it fits on a tabletop I love to play it and try it out! On this channel you will learn about new and older games, I will teach you how to set up the game and how to play it. 

I will show you brand new board games that will launch on Kickstarter but also games that you will find in store.
But it´s not just games, occasionally I paint miniatures and give you a step-by-step on how to paint your own minis. Every now and then I also show some amazing tabletop terrain and game mats,  to level up your gaming experience!  I simply love the world of miniatures, board games, card games, role play and I want to share that love with you! So come join me!  

Videos are released every week so be sure you subscribe to the channel not to miss out.  :)  

#boardgame #tabletop #boardgamereview #tabletopterrain #miniatures #boardgamegeek #tabletopgames #gamer

snippet.title: Learn Code By Gaming
snippet.description:
I enjoy helping beginners learn how to program. My belief is that people learn coding best when they're building things and having fun doing it... and video games are great for that! This channel will focus on programming tutorials for beginners (always with a gaming slant), as well as my thoughts about the software industry.

I offer 1-on-1 coaching: learncodebygaming.com/services
I also do contracting/consulting for software development: clockmaker.ai

- Ben

snippet.title: Gaming Off The Grid
snippet.description: This channel was founded on Robert and Wes’s love for co-op gaming. Literally, the idea for this channel was born with a cold beer in one hand and a light gun in the other. Gaming Off the Grid focuses on gaming together with friends, offline. This new channel offers high quality weekly content that covers a wide array of gaming topics and reviews a new beer in every upload. From the retro gaming to the modern gaming scene, this channel has you covered. This tag team brings their high energy and passion to every episode. So, sit back, relax, pour yourself a beer if you care to and welcome to Gaming Off the Grid.
